            "id": "888ee735b456448c8d947",
            "questionText": "A research team observes a distant galaxy exhibiting significant redshift in its light spectrum, indicating it is moving away from Earth. They measure its recession speed to be $!$700\\ \\text{ km/s }$!$ and its distance to be $!$10\\ \\text{ Mpc }$!$. Given that $!$1\\ \\text{ Mpc } = 3.086 \\times 10^{19}\\ \\text{ km }$!$ and $!$1\\ \\text{ year } = 3.1536 \\times 10^7\\ \\text{ s }$!$, calculate the approximate age of the Universe in years based on this data.",
            "imageText": "",
            "steps": [
                {
                    "id": "188d9952ea8448ec948b1",
                    "stepText": "Let's start by identifying the proper conversion factor to change the distance from megaparsecs (Mpc) to kilometers (km). Which one of the following options is correct?",
                    "stepText2": "",
                    "stepImage": "",
                    "stepSolveAnswer": [
                        ""
                    ],
                    "stepSolveAnswerUnits": "",
                    "stepConcepts": [],
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "optionText": "$!$1 \\ \\text{ Mpc } = 3.086 \\times 10^{19}\\ \\text{ km }$!$",
                            "optionImage": "",
                            "isCorrect": true
                        },
                        {
                            "optionText": "$!$1 \\ \\text{ Mpc } = 3.086 \\times 10^{18}\\ \\text{ km }$!$",
                            "optionImage": "",
                            "isCorrect": false
                        },
                        {
                            "optionText": "$!$1 \\ \\text{ Mpc } = 3.086 \\times 10^{20}\\ \\text{ km }$!$",
                            "optionImage": "",
                            "isCorrect": false
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "f676240b5d41470587c6f",
                    "stepText": "Now convert 10 Mpc to kilometers using the conversion factor from the previous step.",
                    "stepText2": "",
                    "stepImage": "",
                    "stepSolveAnswer": [
                        "3.086e20"
                    ],
                    "stepSolveAnswerUnits": "km",
                    "stepConcepts": [],
                    "options": []
                },
                {
                    "id": "80412f933eb54b4f9b4a4",
